title: Harry Jowsey Is Too Hot To Handle
description:
Lala stepped out Saturday night to a party at TomTom for one of the writers of the HBO series, “Euphoria,” and suffered an emotional hangover the next day. She’s also texting a new cute boy, and shares some deets! Plus, Harry Jowsey is a tiktok star who got his start on the Netflix dating show “Too Hot To Handle.” He and Lala go toes on dating, sex, relationships, and reality TV! And yes, Harry is definitely too hot to handle in case you were wondering.
